<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV84">
<l>piṉpiṟakka vaittaṉaṉko laṉṟiniṉṟu taṉkaḻaṟ</l>
<l>kaṉpuṟaikka vaittanāḷa ṟintaṉaṉko lāḻiyāṉ</l>
<l>tantiṟatto raṉpilāva ṟivilāta nāyiṉē</l>
<l>ṉeṉṟiṟatti leṉkolempi rāṉkuṟippil vaittatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Did [the Lord] with the discus make [me] be born again?</l>
<l>Or did He intend the day on which [He] will cause love for Him</l>
<l rend="indent">to become firm [in me, with me] remaining at His feet?</l>
<l>How come our Lord has kept me, a dog devoid of love for Him or knowledge,</l>
<l rend="indent">in [His] mind?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
